{
  "key": "ontology:innovation_ecosystem",
  "label": "Innovation Ecosystem Ontology",
  "version": 1,
  "domain": "financial_services",
  "notes": "Volume XI pack (ADR-0014) for the innovation half of the VC / CU / fintech / innovation stack \u2014 the Cooperative Markets graph that connects credit unions and innovation companies. Enriches the innovation_ecosystem family (startup, founder, product, technology, pilot, proof_of_concept, integration, partnership, capability, market_category, vendor_evaluation, innovation_score, institution_readiness, startup_readiness, investment_thesis, investment_committee_memo). The partnership object carries the discovery->evaluation->pilot->integration->partnership->investment->monitoring relationship ladder. Relationship targets are catalog schema_refs (closed graph). innovation_score is a Dispatch inference (calculation), not a weights-only conclusion \u2014 evidence/source/confidence/lineage are persisted per doctrine. Connector keys are forward references into the Connector Registry (Volume IX); required_document and KPI keys are free-form.",
